desc_long								关于这款游戏							The sequel to Inferno+, Radiangames' critically-acclaimed twin-stick action-RPG, arrives on PC at last! INFERNO 2 boasts even more devious levels, more weapons, more upgrades and powers, more enemies, and more customization, along with more insane explosions and particle effects.BIGGER, BETTER, BADDER! Inferno 2 on PC is everything Radiangames fans have been waiting for:* Play through 80+ levels of atmospheric awesomeness* New Game+ mode adds even more replayability* Customizable gamepad and KB/mouse controls* 3 difficulty levels (change it up at any time)* Dozens of enemy types* All-new special level types and goals* Tons of secrets to discover* A large arsenal of upgrade-able weapons and ship powers* Beautiful HD graphics* Steam Achievements						
